Hehehe♡ This is the best♡ My Master♡
Sadi, hehehe... Now, Merill. \c[27] Give your \c[0] report.

Yes... The preparations for the advance on \c[14]Variante\c[0],
centered around the real Merill and Hayato, are complete♡

Most of the officials in Variante have been won over, so there's
no problem attacking at any time♡
Sadi, is that so? Then let's quickly take control of this place♡

And the matter of Seria's \c[14]Holy Sword\c[0] is also being
arranged at the Demon King's army headquarters.

Sadi, that will become a splendid force...♡ Seria, we'll have you
be useful♡

..........................Understood, Master♡ \c[27]Everything is for the sake of
paradise\c[0]♡

.......................And so, the small war between the succubus and the girls came to
an end.

【Hayato's Aftermath】 Teamed up with Merill, they advanced to
Variante. On his days off, he is being pampered by having sex
with Merill every day.

【Merill's Aftermath】 She seduced and captured the people of
Variante with her charm. It seems she was entrusted with the
control of this city by Sadi.

【Sadi's Aftermath】 Having Seria and Hayato in her grasp, she is
currently expanding her influence. She has become the most
powerful monster among the Demon King's army executives.

【Seria's Aftermath】 After adjusting the \c[14]Holy Sword\c[0], she
becomes a force of chaos on the human side, serving as Sadi's
bitch and the most powerful weapon.
The \c[14]paper\c[0] I dropped at the church that day...
It was a love letter that I had stopped writing halfway through.
Thank you for playing. Moving to the reminiscence room.
